Conditionls : are used when you need to do something depending on conditions 
   there are three conditionals 
       1)if
       2)elif
       3)else 
 Syntex for conditionals is :
  ==> and in every line of required conditions to satisfied we should use space before it that space is called indentation.
      if IF condition is satisfied then running will stop or it will check next condition elif then else 
      

